DIA_Ingolf_Q602_City_03_01: Let's not waste time, we have to find Ulryk and the Usurer!
DIA_Ingolf_Q602_City_03_02: True to our word - we have arrived. Adanos must have been watching over us, because I see we got here at the last minute!
DIA_Ingolf_Q602_City_03_03: I just want to thank you for all you have done for our island.
DIA_Ingolf_Q602_City_03_04: We'll make sure there are no more enemies in the city. Let us only hope that leaderless they surrender without a fight... Go after the Usurer and may Adanos be with you!
